Ratio and Proportion- Part 1 | L:6 | Campus Recruitment Training | Aptitude | GATE | RBR

What is Ratio?
It is a comparision of 2 like items.
It is same as fraction.
a/b is written as a:b
a is antecedent; b is consequent.

What is proportion?
It is an equality between 2 ratios.
a:b = c:d
a/b = c/d
ad = cb

